<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lectia 3: Crearea unei baze de date in Access | Clasa 8</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-primary: #0a0a12;
            --bg-secondary: #12121f;
            --bg-card: #1a1a2e;
            --accent-red: #ef4444;
            --accent-rose: #f43f5e;
            --accent-green: #10b981;
            --accent-orange: #f59e0b;
            --accent-cyan: #06b6d4;
            --accent-purple: #8b5cf6;
            --accent-blue: #3b82f6;
            --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
            --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --border: #2d2d44;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .nav-back {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .nav-back:hover { color: var(--accent-cyan); }

        .progress-steps {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .step {
            width: 60px;
            height: 8px;
            background: var(--border);
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .step.active { background: var(--accent-red); }
        .step.completed { background: var(--accent-green); }

        .section {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        .section.active { display: block; }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .goal-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15), rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1));
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .goal-icon { font-size: 5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

        .goal-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .goal-desc {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
        }

        .try-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15), rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1));
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-orange);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .try-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .try-badge {
            background: var(--accent-orange);
            color: #000;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .challenge-box {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .challenge-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-orange);
        }

        .challenge-task {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-orange);
        }

        .hint-box {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-purple);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .hint-toggle {
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--accent-purple);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hint-content {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .hint-content.show { display: block; }

        .learn-section {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .learn-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .learn-badge {
            background: var(--accent-red);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .concept-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-red);
        }

        .concept-name {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-cyan);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .concept-def {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .steps-list {
            counter-reset: step;
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .steps-list li {
            counter-increment: step;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .steps-list li::before {
            content: counter(step);
            background: var(--accent-red);
            color: white;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .keyboard-key {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .menu-path {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: monospace;
            color: var(--accent-cyan);
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .data-types-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .data-type-item {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .data-type-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-purple);
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .data-type-desc {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .test-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15), rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1));
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-purple);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .test-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .test-badge {
            background: var(--accent-purple);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .quiz-question {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .question-text {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .options {
            display: grid;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .option {
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .option:hover { border-color: var(--accent-purple); }
        .option.selected { border-color: var(--accent-red); background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); }
        .option.correct { border-color: var(--accent-green); background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2); }
        .option.wrong { border-color: var(--accent-red); background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); }

        .feedback {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            display: none;
        }

        .feedback.success {
            display: block;
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-green);
            color: var(--accent-green);
        }

        .feedback.error {
            display: block;
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-red);
            color: var(--accent-red);
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-red), var(--accent-rose));
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-green), var(--accent-cyan));
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-red);
            color: var(--accent-red);
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .completion {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
        }

        .completion-icon { font-size: 5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

        .completion-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .xp-gain {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-orange);
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-red);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .warning-box strong {
            color: var(--accent-red);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container { padding: 1rem; }
            .goal-title { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .actions { flex-direction: column; }
            .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../../assets/css/mobile.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../../assets/css/mobile-first.css">
    <!-- PoW System Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../../assets/css/pow.css">
</head>
<body>
    <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Sari la continut</a>
    <div id="main-content" class="container">
        <div class="progress-steps">
            <div class="step active" data-step="goal" title="Obiectiv"></div>
            <div class="step" data-step="try" title="Incearca"></div>
            <div class="step" data-step="learn" title="Invata"></div>
            <div class="step" data-step="test" title="Verifica"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- GOAL Section -->
        <div class="section active" id="goal">
            <div class="goal-section">
                <div class="goal-icon">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
                <h1 class="goal-title">Vreau sa creez prima mea baza de date!</h1>
                <p class="goal-desc">
                    Dupa aceasta lectie, vei sti sa deschizi Access, sa creezi o baza de date noua si sa adaugi un tabel cu campuri.
                </p>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="goToStep('try')">
                    Sa incepem! ‚Üí
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TRY Section -->
        <div class="section" id="try">
            <div class="try-section">
                <div class="try-header">
                    <span class="try-badge">INCEARCA</span>
                    <h2>Exploreaza Access!</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="challenge-box">
                    <div class="challenge-title">Provocarea ta (5 minute):</div>
                    <div class="challenge-task">
                        <strong>1.</strong> Deschide Microsoft Access (Start ‚Üí cauta "Access")<br><br>
                        <strong>2.</strong> Click pe "Blank database" (Baza de date goala)<br><br>
                        <strong>3.</strong> Alege un nume: "ScoalaMea" si salveaza pe Desktop<br><br>
                        <strong>4.</strong> Exploreaza interfata - ce butoane vezi?
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hint-box">
                    <div class="hint-toggle" onclick="toggleHint(this)">
                        Nu gasesti Access? Click aici
                    </div>
                    <div class="hint-content">
                        <p>Access face parte din Microsoft Office. Daca nu il ai, poti folosi versiunea online sau cere profesorului sa il instaleze.</p>
                        <p>Alternativ, poti urmari lectia teoretic si practica la scoala.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="actions">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="goToStep('goal')">‚Üê Inapoi</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="goToStep('learn')">
                        Am explorat! Arata-mi cum ‚Üí
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- LEARN Section -->
        <div class="section" id="learn">
            <div class="learn-section">
                <div class="learn-header">
                    <span class="learn-badge">INVATA</span>
                    <h2>Crearea unei baze de date in Access</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="concept-card">
                    <div class="concept-name">Pasul 1: Deschide Access si creeaza baza de date</div>
                    <div class="concept-def">
                        <ol class="steps-list">
                            <li>
                                <div>
                                    Apasa <span class="keyboard-key">Win</span> si scrie "Access", apoi <span class="keyboard-key">Enter</span>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div>
                                    Click pe <strong>"Blank database"</strong> (prima optiune)
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div>
                                    Scrie numele bazei de date (ex: "Elevi") si alege locatia (Desktop)
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div>
                                    Click <strong>"Create"</strong> - Access va deschide baza de date goala
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="warning-box">
                    <strong>Important!</strong> Fisierele Access au extensia <code>.accdb</code>. Nu sterge sau muta acest fisier - contine toate datele tale!
                </div>

                <div class="concept-card" style="border-color: var(--accent-purple);">
                    <div class="concept-name">Pasul 2: Creeaza primul tabel</div>
                    <div class="concept-def">
                        Cand creezi o baza de date noua, Access deschide automat un tabel gol numit "Table1". Trebuie sa:
                        <ol class="steps-list" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                            <li>
                                <div>
                                    Mergi la tab-ul <strong>"Design View"</strong> (sau click dreapta pe Table1 ‚Üí Design View)
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div>
                                    Access te va intreba sa salvezi tabelul - scrie un nume descriptiv: <strong>"Elevi"</strong>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div>
                                    Acum poti adauga campurile (coloanele) tabelului
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="concept-card" style="border-color: var(--accent-orange);">
                    <div class="concept-name">Pasul 3: Adauga campuri</div>
                    <div class="concept-def">
                        In Design View, pentru fiecare camp trebuie sa specifici:
                        <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 1.5rem;">
                            <li><strong>Field Name</strong> - numele campului (ex: Nume, Prenume)</li>
                            <li><strong>Data Type</strong> - tipul de date (text, numar, data)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 style="margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem; color: var(--accent-cyan);">Tipuri de date comune:</h3>

                <div class="data-types-grid">
                    <div class="data-type-item">
                        <div class="data-type-name">Short Text</div>
                        <div class="data-type-desc">Text scurt (max 255 caractere) - Nume, Prenume, Oras</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="data-type-item">
                        <div class="data-type-name">Number</div>
                        <div class="data-type-desc">Numere intregi sau zecimale - Varsta, Nota, Pret</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="data-type-item">
                        <div class="data-type-name">Date/Time</div>
                        <div class="data-type-desc">Date si ore - DataNasterii, DataInscrierii</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="data-type-item">
                        <div class="data-type-name">AutoNumber</div>
                        <div class="data-type-desc">Numar care creste automat - ideal pentru ID (cheie primara)</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="data-type-item">
                        <div class="data-type-name">Yes/No</div>
                        <div class="data-type-desc">Valori de tip da/nu - Activ, Platit, Prezent</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="data-type-item">
                        <div class="data-type-name">Long Text</div>
                        <div class="data-type-desc">Text lung - Descriere, Observatii, Note</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="concept-card" style="border-color: var(--accent-green);">
                    <div class="concept-name">Exemplu practic: Tabelul Elevi</div>
                    <div class="concept-def">
                        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                            <thead>
                                <tr style="background: var(--accent-red); color: white;">
                                    <th style="padding: 0.5rem; text-align: left;">Field Name</th>
                                    <th style="padding: 0.5rem; text-align: left;">Data Type</th>
                                    <th style="padding: 0.5rem; text-align: left;">Explicatie</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
                                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">ID</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">AutoNumber</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Cheie primara (se completeaza singur)</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Nume</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Short Text</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Numele de familie</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Prenume</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Short Text</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Prenumele elevului</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">DataNasterii</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Date/Time</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Cand s-a nascut</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Clasa</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">Short Text</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">8A, 8B, etc.</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="concept-card" style="border-color: var(--accent-cyan);">
                    <div class="concept-name">Pasul 4: Seteaza cheia primara</div>
                    <div class="concept-def">
                        In Design View:
                        <ol style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.5rem;">
                            <li>Click pe randul cu campul ID</li>
                            <li>Click pe butonul <strong>"Primary Key"</strong> din toolbar (sau click dreapta ‚Üí Primary Key)</li>
                            <li>Vei vedea o cheita langa campul ID</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="concept-card" style="border-color: var(--accent-orange);">
                    <div class="concept-name">Pasul 5: Salveaza si adauga date</div>
                    <div class="concept-def">
                        <ol style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.5rem;">
                            <li>Apasa <span class="keyboard-key">Ctrl</span> + <span class="keyboard-key">S</span> pentru a salva tabelul</li>
                            <li>Schimba in <strong>"Datasheet View"</strong> (View ‚Üí Datasheet View)</li>
                            <li>Acum poti introduce date in tabel - scrie in celule!</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="actions">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="goToStep('try')">‚Üê Inapoi</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="goToStep('test')">
                        Am inteles! Testeaza-ma ‚Üí
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TEST Section -->
        <div class="section" id="test">
            <div class="test-section">
                <div class="test-header">
                    <span class="test-badge">VERIFICA</span>
                    <h2>Hai sa vedem ce ai retinut!</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="quiz-question" id="q1">
                    <div class="question-text">1. Ce tip de date folosesti pentru un camp care trebuie sa se completeze automat cu numere unice?</div>
                    <div class="options">
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q1', false)">Number</div>
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q1', true)">AutoNumber</div>
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q1', false)">Short Text</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback" id="q1-feedback"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="quiz-question" id="q2">
                    <div class="question-text">2. Ce extensie au fisierele Access?</div>
                    <div class="options">
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q2', false)">.docx</div>
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q2', false)">.xlsx</div>
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q2', true)">.accdb</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback" id="q2-feedback"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="quiz-question" id="q3">
                    <div class="question-text">3. In ce view definesti campurile si tipurile de date pentru un tabel?</div>
                    <div class="options">
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q3', true)">Design View</div>
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q3', false)">Datasheet View</div>
                        <div class="option" onclick="selectOption(this, 'q3', false)">Form View</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback" id="q3-feedback"></div>
                </div>

                <div id="test-result" style="display: none;"></div>

                <div class="actions">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="goToStep('learn')">‚Üê Inapoi la lectie</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="checkAllAnswers()">
                        Verifica raspunsurile
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
